<br />
<br />For the pitch bends, if anyone wants to do a slow or shallow one, it would almost have to be a lot finer than a semitone.  Like playing a guitar, it's probably more common to bend the string and stay in the same fret instead of sliding up/down the fretboard, heheh.

		

